# Aesthetic numbers

Ds ← "0123456789abcdef"

IsAesth ← /×=1⌵⧈-≡⨂¤Ds
Aesths  ← ⊸≡◇IsAesth≡⌟(□⇌˜⊏Ds⊥) ↘2⇡17

≡(□▽)∩⍉≡Aesths+1⇡6000        # Generate enough candidates.
⟜≡(□↙⊙↘⊃(+1×2|-1×4)⊙°□)+2⇡⊸⧻ # Take required number of each.
≡(&p&p$"Base _")             # Print them.

&p$"\nBase 10, 1000-9999\n_"▽⊸≡◇IsAesth°⋕↘1000⇡10000
# ▽⊸≡◇IsAesth°⋕+1e8⇡0.3e8 # A waste of time and space.
